column1: These data are consistent with data reported to CDC for Abortion Surveillance -- United States, 2011 found at http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/pdf/ss/ss6311.pdf
"--"  Reporting area did not report, or data not reportable by CDC.

** Reporting area did not report, or only reported by occurrence; because abortion numbers by residence are available only from other reporting areas where residents obtained abortions, data by state of maternal residence should be interpreted with caution.
